{"tid":281472,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"想死","createTime":"2017-06-12T17:53:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T18:00:10.000Z","uid":66532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd0ec7d220436a92ebe632f4b37e4d9e6425e353","tid":281472,"uid":66532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:53:54.000Z","msg":"是噉的，小弟今年year2 <br />\n<br />\nsem1 嗰時兩星期考十個subject<br />\n就發現超級唔夠時間溫書，因為量太多，範圍太大<br />\n而當中有啲科係由幾個細科combine埋當一科噉計<br />\n噉所以就考得一般(未算pass但未到1st<br />\n然後sem2見到只係考兩科，另外兩科冇考試<br />\n就覺得好輕鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，點知係惡夢嘅開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n話說過去依幾日就已經考完嗰兩科<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每科都可以話得三年試卷操<br />\n見到都係得兩三個題型，所以操起上嚟比較容易<br />\n<br />\n點知真係落場考嗰時就發現 今年啲卷所考嘅題目同過往考嘅一啲都唔相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後就發現操pp卷係一啲幫助都冇<br />\n同時見到考場大部分考生開卷嗰時都拗曬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為報master要用year 2&amp; 3啲分，會影響到前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n噉畀佢搞法真係好想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求開解"},{"pid":"f23110c12f5a3f377f0a8b0938f2e71f96a055cb","tid":281472,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:57:44.000Z","msg":"開解"},{"pid":"e25c194cc10e2998c547fbb41c6c8c93422c30bc","tid":281472,"uid":66532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T17:59:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開解</blockquote><br />\n多謝膊頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82a15ccf437bfdd8ad6a2d0fa306e6341b2c6c8","tid":281472,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T18:00:10.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 讀書好難 唔好輕生"}]}